ympiacos]]'''\n|[[Panathinaikos VC|Panathinaikos]]\n| <center>19\u20133 (57)</center>\n|-\n| <center>[[2010\u201311 Volleyleague (Greece)|2010\u201311]]</center>\n|[[Iraklis V.C. (Thessaloniki)|Iraklis]]\n| <center>0\u20133</center>\n|style=\"background:#FFFF99\"|'''[[Olympiacos S.C.|Olympiacos]]'''\n|[[Iraklis V.C. (Thessaloniki)|Iraklis]]\n| <center>17\u20135 (52)</center>\n|-\n| <center>[[2011\u201312 Volleyleague (Greece)|2011\u201312]]</center>\n|style=\"background:#FFFF99\"|'''[[Iraklis V.C. (Thessaloniki)|Iraklis]]'''\n| <center>3\u20132</center>\n|[[Foinikas Syros V.C.|Foinikas Syros]]\n|[[Iraklis V.C. (Thessaloniki)|Iraklis]]\n| <center>18\u20132 (50)</center>\n|-\n| <center>[[2012\u201313 Volleyleague (Greece)|2012\u201313]]</center>\n|style=\"background:#FFFF99\"|'''[[Olympiacos S.C.|Olympiacos]]'''\n| <center>3\u20131</center>\n|[[Pamvohaikos VC|Pamvohaikos]]\n|[[Olympiacos S.C.|Olympiacos]]\n| <center>20\u20132 (56)</center>\n|-\n| <center>[[2013\u201314 Volleyleague (Greece)|2013\u201314]]</center>\n|style=\"background:#FFFF99\"|'''[[Olympiacos S.C.|Olympiacos]]'''\n| <center>3\u20130</center>\n|[[Ethnikos Alexandroupolis V.C.|Ethnikos Alexandroupolis]]\n|[[Olympiacos S.C.|Olympiacos]]\n| <center>17\u20135 (52)</center>\n|-\n| <center>[[2014\u201315 Volleyleague (Greece)|2014\u201315]]</center>\n|style=\"background:#FFFF99\"|'''[[P.A.O.K. Thessaloniki V.C.|PAOK]]'''\n| <center>3\u20130</center>\n|[[Olympiacos S.C.|Olympiacos]]\n|[[P.A.O.K. Thessaloniki V.C.|PAOK]]\n| <center>20\u20132 (57)</center>\n|-\n| <center>[[2015\u201316 Volleyleague (Greece)|2015\u201316]]</center>\n|[[Foinikas Syros V.C.|Foinikas Syros]]\n| <center>1\u20133</center>\n|style=\"background:#FFFF99\"|'''[[P.A.O.K. Thessaloniki V.C.|PAOK]]'''\n|[[Olympiacos S.C.|Olympiacos]]\n| <center>20\u20132 (59)</center>\n|-\n| <center>[[2016\u201317 Volleyleague (Greece)|2016\u201317]]</center>\n|[[Olympiacos S.C.|Olympiacos]]\n| <center>2\u20133</center>\n|style=\"background:#FFFF99\"|'''[[P