 Ivanovs]]\n|1992\u20132001\n|69\n|1\n|-\n|17.\n|align=\"left\"|[[Dzintars Zirnis]]\n|1997\u20132010\n|67\n|0\n|-\n|18.\n|align=\"left\"|[[Oskars K\u013cava]]\n|2005\u20132013\n|65\n|1\n|-\n|19.\n|align=\"left\"|[[\u0112riks P\u0113tersons]]\n|1929\u20131939\n|63\n|24\n|-\n|20.\n|align=\"left\"|'''[[Deniss Ivanovs]]'''\n|2003\u20132013\n|60\n|2\n|-\n|}\n:''Players in '''bold''' are still active.''\n\n===Top goalscorers===\n*Latvia goalscoring record\n{{main|Progression of Latvia association football goalscoring record}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\" cellpadding=\"3\" style=\"text-align: center;\"\n|-\n!#\n!Player\n!Career\n!Goals (Caps)\n|-\n|1.\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[M\u0101ris Verpakovskis]]\n|1999\u20132014\n|29 (104)\n|-\n|2.\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[\u0112riks P\u0113tersons]]\n|1929\u20131939\n|24 (63)\n|-\n|3.\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Vit\u0101lijs Astafjevs]]\n|1992\u20132010\n|16 (167)\n|-\n|rowspan=2|4.\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Marians Pahars]]\n|1996\u20132007\n|15 (75)\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Juris Laiz\u0101ns]]\n|1998\u20132013\n|15 (113)\n|-\n|6.\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Alberts \u0160eibelis]]\n|1925\u20131939\n|14 (54)\n|-\n|7.\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[I\u013cja Vestermans]]\n|1935\u20131938\n|13 (23)\n|-\n|rowspan=3|8.\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Aleksandrs Cau\u0146a]]\n|2007\u20132015\n|12 (45)\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|'''[[Val\u0113rijs \u0160abala]]'''\n|2013\u2013present\n|12 (52)\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Mihails Zem\u013cinskis]]\n|1992\u20132005\n|12 (105)\n|-\n|11.\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[V\u012bts Rimkus]]\n|1995\u20132008\n|11 (73)\n|-\n|rowspan=2|12.\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Arnolds Tauri\u0146\u0161]]\n|1925\u20131935\n|10 (39)\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Imants Bleidelis]]\n|1995\u20132007\n|10 (106)\n|-\n|rowspan=6|14.\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[\u0100dolfs S\u012bmanis]]\n|1932\u20131940\n|9 (9)\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Voldem\u0101rs Plade]]\n|1923\u20131929\n|9 (16)\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Aleksandrs Vanags]]\n|1937\u20131940\n|9 (18)\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[\u0122irts Karlsons]]\n|2003\u20132017\n|9 (51)\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|'''[[Aleksejs Vi\u0161\u0146akovs]]'''\n|2004\u2013present\n|9 (81)\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Andrejs Rubins]]\n|1998\u20132011\n|9 (117)\n|-\n|rowspan=2|20.\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Vaclavs Bordu\u0161ko]]\n|1934\u20131939\n|8 (25)\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Ark\u0101dijs Pavlovs]]\n|1924\u20131933\n|8 (37)\n|}\n:''Players in '''bold''' are still active.''\n\n===Hat-tricks===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Player !! style=\"text-align:center\" | Competition !! Against !! style=\"text-align:center\" | Home/Away !! style=\"text-align:center;\"| Result !! Date\n|-\n| {{sortname|Voldem\u0101rs \u017dins||}}|| style=\"text-align:center;\"| International Friendly ||{{flagicon|LIT}} [[Lithuania national football team|Lithuania]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| Home || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 6\u20133||{{dts|format=dmy|1927|7|27}}\n|-\n| {{sortname|Voldem\u0101rs Plade||}}|| style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[1929 Baltic Cup]] ||{{flagicon|LIT}} [[Lithuania national football team|Lithuania]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| Home || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 3\u20131||{{dts|format=dmy|1929|8|14}}\n|-\n| {{sortname|\u0112riks P\u0113tersons||}}|| style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[1930 Baltic Cup]] ||{{flagicon|LIT}} [[Lithuania national football team|Lithuania]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| Away || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 3\u20133||{{dts|format=dmy|1930|8|17}}\n|-\n| {{sortname|\u0112riks P\u0113tersons||}}<sup> 4</sup> || style=\"text-align:center;\"| International Friendly ||{{flagicon|LIT}} [[Lithuania national football team|Lithuania]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| Home || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 5\u20132||{{dts|format=dmy|1931|6|30}}\n|-\n| {{sortname|\u0112riks P\u0113tersons||}}|| style=